title: Grateful Dead Live at Alpine Valley Music Theatre on 1982-08-08
description:
Set 1

Alabama Getaway-> Promised Land, They Love Each Other, Mama Tried-> Mexicali Blues, Loser-> Little Red Rooster, Brown Eyed Women, Looks Like Rain, Peggy-O, Samson & Delilah

Set 2

Far From Me-> Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain-> Estimated Prophet-> Drums*-> The Other One**-> Not Fade Away**-> Wharf Rat**-> Good Lovin'**, E: Satisfaction**-> E: Brokedown Palace**

*W Zakir Hussain, **Other artist(s): with John Cippolina

reviews.review_text: warning Loser still has tape warp Sounds like an electrical/power problem with the recording device, during Loser.
